column5: Glad you made it back safely Bubba. You have a good rest and we'll catch ya later. It was nice seeing you again.

Right on my southern brotha bubba..  Thanks for showing me how to skin a catfish and introducing us to that wonderful nectar..  Moonshine..  OOH I can still feel it eating away at my gut LOL.  cheers HD
Good to here Glen..... Thanx for bringin all that shine with ya bubba !!!
It was great finally meeting you Glen.  Hopefully, next time will be for a little bit longer. Glad to hear you got home safely.
Good to hear sweetie.  Glad you made it safe and sound.  Let us know if Les made it aswell.  Joey
we are glad to hear you made it safely miss kelly misses ya all  yes she misses you to roy!!! but she did ask where the pictures were-lol
Glad to hear you made it back safe and sound bud. Sorry I couldn't make it up this time.
I can smell ya from here,dawg!
Was wonderin if y'all made it back.Sorry I couldn't make it up there. Joe
Glad to hear you are back at home safely Glen.  Get some well deserved rest!!!
Hey that one's mine jigga!  HAHAAH
Glad you made er back safe and sound Dawg !! Nice too see you again and thanks for picking that rod holder up for me!! Oh ya and the shine Cheers buddy looking forward to your report!!!! BMM
Man you must love canada driving all that way and hours nice to hear you made it home safe. Looking forward to your report .BTW nice hat I should get me one with the way my summer is going.
